wiki.summary: On “WITHOUT YOU,” The Kid LAROI portrays what a love-hate relationship looks like, communicating his feelings towards a girl on the track while dealing with the struggles of a heartbreak. LAROI sings over a slow, guitar-based instrumental produced by frequent collaborator and producer Omer Fedi, as well as Blake Slatkin. Read more on Last.fm.
